.email-container
  .email-header
    %a{href: 'http://parti.xyz'}
      %img{src: asset_url('logo_parti_slogan_white_2.png'), style: 'max-width: 100%;'}
  .email-content.text-center
    %p #{@resource.nickname} 님, 회원가입을 축하드려요!
    %p 이제 유쾌한 민주주의 플랫폼, 빠띠를 즐겨보세요.
    %p 아래 링크를 클릭하시면 등록하신 계정이 확인됩니다.
    %p= link_to '확인하기', confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token), class: 'btn-email'
  .email-footer
    %div{:style => "text-align: left; position: relative; margin: auto; max-width: 600px;"}
      %div{style: 'margin-left: 30px; float: left'}
        %a{href: 'http://parti.xyz'}
          %img{src: asset_url('parti_logo_white.png'), style: 'max-height: 40px;'}
      %div{:style => "float: left; margin: 0 30px; line-height: 20px;font-size: 90%;"}
        %a{:href => "http://parti.xyz", :style => "color: #999; text-decoration: none"} parti.xyz
        %br/
        %a{:href => "mailto:help@parti.xyz", :style => "color: #999; text-decoration: none"} help@parti.xyz
      %div{:style => "line-height: 20px;color: #999;font-size: 90%; overflow: hidden"}
        %a{:href => "http://fb.com/parti.xyz", :style => "color: #999; text-decoration: none"} fb.com/parti.xyz
        %br/
        %a{:href => "http://medium.com/parti-xyz-developers", :style => "color: #999; text-decoration: none"} medium.com/parti-xyz-developers
